review_title: Great Product but Description does not match order
reviews: Great Product. It did the trick of holding up a small decorative mirror in my dining room. However I received only three hangers when the listing indicated that the product came with four hangers. A bit disappointed since I needed the four hangers plus it didn't feel like value for my money!

First of all the shipping was so quick and efficient! I was a bit skeptical about using this product on my eyes since I have sensitive skin but it didn't cause any irritation at all. It is so simple to use and so far my lashes look great. I can't wait to see the results after 6 weeks. I will definitely recommend to my friends and even buy as gifts!
I live in Toronto and was able to pick up most local channels. Easy to setup. Impressed to get up to 16 channels on a good day. I would definitely recommend this product.
The carrying strap was not included with my order!
